comments: Ellington (DET) legally contests Sexton's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Stauskas (CLE) makes marginal contact with Ellington's (DET) side as he receives the ball and it does not affect his SQBR.
Maker (DET) jumps vertically and maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with Sexton (CLE) at the end of his drive.
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in Sexton's (CLE) path and does not deliver the contact.
RAR shows Stauskas (CLE) makes contact with Maker's (DET) right arm as the hand-off takes place, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Drummond (DET) fails to fully clear the lane within three seconds.
Zizic (CLE) hedges the pick and maintains legal guarding position as body contact is made with Jackson (DET) along the perimeter.
LAR shows Sexton (CLE) makes marginal lower body contact with Jackson (DET) after the release of his jump shot attempt that does not affect his ability to land safely.
Nwaba (CLE) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Nwaba (CLE) and Maker (DET) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
RAR shows Osman (CLE) makes lower body contact with Galloway (DET) following the release of his jump shot attempt, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to land safely.
Nwaba (CLE) engages with Maker (DET) as the shot is released, but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Maker (DET) initiates body contact prior to dislodging the ball from Zizic (CLE) after the rebound.
Jackson (DET) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps thereafter.
Sexton (CLE) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Jackson (DET) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) makes marginal contact with Maker's (DET) side during rebounding.
Maker (DET) makes marginal contact with Stauskas' (CLE) right arm that does not affect his SQBR or ability to maintain control of the ball.
Galloway (DET) commits the take foul on Osman (CLE).
Ellington (DET) sets the screen on Nwaba (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nwaba (CLE) makes clean contact with the ball prior to the incidental contact to Jackson's (DET) body on the perimeter.
Galloway (DET) commits the take foul on Stauskas (CLE).
